The annual A da Road Race organised by Run/Walk for Life is back and interested athletes are advised to enter soonest. The race will be hosted from Laerskool Pietersburg-Noord Primary on the corner of Biccard and Rissik streets on 20 May and is scheduled to start at 07:00. The race offers a 5 km fun run and 10 km and 15 km road race options. Entry fees are R30, R50 and R70 respectively. The 10 km and 15 km race will start at 07:00 followed by the 5 km 15 minutes later. Temporary licences are available at R30. For entries and more information contact Kobie Marais on 082 561 5429. Story: RC Myburgh &gt;&gt;rc.observer@gmail.com &nbsp;